\f0\b\fs64 \cf2 \cb3 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MSLIB \'96 Multi-Skilled Resource-Constrained Project Library\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 MSLIB \'96 Project datasets for the 
\f2\b Multi-Skilled Resource-Constrained Project Scheduling Problem (MSRCPSP)
\f1\b0 . Includes various datasets, Excel summaries with network/resource/skill indicators and best-known solutions for multiple versions of the MSRCPSP useful for benchmarking and algorithm testing.\cb1 \
\cb3 The story of how datasets for the resource-constrained project scheduling problem were generated is described in the book {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-031-71507-5"}}{\fldrslt 
\f3\i \cf4 \ul \ulc4 A Quest for Projects with Scarce Resources: Seeking Schedule Intelligence Through Project Data Discovery}}.\cb1 \
\cb3 The 
\f2\b MSRCPSP
\f1\b0  is an extension of this well-known problem and is generated as described in the references below. A summary is available {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.projectmanagement.ugent.be/research/data"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 here}}.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \cb6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs48 \cf2 \cb3 Problem Overview\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 The 
\f2\b MSRCPSP
\f1\b0  is a fundamental project scheduling problem aiming to 
\f2\b minimize total project duration while respecting resource constraints
\f1\b0 . It is widely studied and forms the basis for countless solution procedures in project scheduling research.\cb1 \
\cb3 Extensions of the problem focus on other objectives (e.g. 
\f2\b cost
\f1\b0 ) and include additional 
\f2\b skill features
\f1\b0 .\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \cb6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

