\f4\b\fs48 \cf2 \cb3 Dataset Overview\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 The 
\f2\b MSLIB library
\f1\b0  contains five project datasets in subfolders, as follows:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MSLIB1 (6,600 instances)
\f1\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Basic set for research on the 
\f2\b MSRCPSP
\f1\b0 .\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MSLIB2 (9,000 instances)
\f1\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Set with a wide range of projects with a smaller but still diversified set of 
\f2\b multi-skilled workforces
\f1\b0 .\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MSLIB3 (11,880 instances)
\f1\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Set with a substantial set of 
\f2\b small and large workforces
\f1\b0 , with variability in both 
\f2\b skill availability
\f1\b0  and the 
\f2\b breadth of the resources
\f1\b0 .\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MSLIB4 (5,000 instances)
\f1\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Set composed of the 
\f2\b hardest instances
\f1\b0  with projects of 
\f2\b 30 activities
\f1\b0 .\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
MSLIB5 (growing number of instances)
\f1\b0 \cb1 \uc0\u8232 
\f2\b \cb3 Empirical dataset
\f1\b0  (read the MSLIB_INFO_FILE.rtf for more explanation)\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \cb6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

